  <brief_title>Videolaryngoscopy in Patients With Cervical Spine Immobilisation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised Crossover Trial Comparing the McGrath Series 5 Videolaryngoscope With the Macintosh Laryngoscope in Patients With Cervical Spine Immobilisation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
